{
  "stem": "12491.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I fished out meat, I traded it for a piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So this was my [INAUDIBLE] grounds.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Eventually, after the fence was built, I was moved into the factory.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I was still an electrician.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I became in charge of one shift.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "There were two or three shifts of working.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "One shift in charge of electric ovens, which were annealing in material from which we were the Schindler's camp was to produce ammunition.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Annealing means softening of the metal so it can be drawn in large presses.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "The product which we were supposed to be making-- which we were making- were tips of anti-armor shells.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They consisted of a-- they were shaped-- a conical shape about 12 inches or 14 inches long to a sharp point.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And at the opposite end, it had a female thread which was to mate with another part made in some other place.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We were not to make up the other part.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "We were only to ship these parts which we were manufacturing to the factory somewhere else, which would assemble them.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "As I was told later, Schindler was changing the drawings to such that none of these parts had correct threads to mate with the parts when they arrived in the other end.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And supposedly, all these months, we were producing worthless merchandise.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "During the time-- approximately December 1944, possibly early January 1945-- I was approached by one of the Jewish prisoners asking was I interested in doing something which will be dangerous, but might save our lives?",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said, describe it to me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Maybe I'm interested.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he described it to me.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
